[assistant] 
[assistant] Commit:
[assistant] - `ec3e33efd8 Avoid persisting javassist proxy instance in native image`
[assistant] 
[assistant] What changed:
[assistant] - `ProxyFixture` no longer stores the generated Javassist proxy instance in a static field.
[assistant] - It now creates the proxy during build-time fixture initialization, serializes it immediately into a `byte[]`, and only persists those serialized bytes in the image heap.
[assistant] - The test deserializes from the stored byte array at runtime, which should still exercise `ProxyObjectInputStream.readClassDescriptor(...)` without embedding the generated proxy object itself into the native image heap.
[assistant] 
[assistant] I did not rerun tests.
